// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0521 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 4d76a626-8987-53c1-be7a-c6a1bd1ed194

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:22.04*")
